\v 15 Izaphila, inikwe okwegolide leShebha\x + 72.10.\x*, ikhulekelwe njalonjalo, usuku lonke ibusiswe\x + Dute. 9.20.\x*.
\v 16 Kuzakuba khona inala yamabele elizweni ezingqongeni zezintaba; izithelo zawo zihatshazele njengeLebhanoni; labomuzi\x + Nani 24.19.\x*\x + 1 Kho. 4.20.\x* bazahluma\x + Hlab. 92.7.\x* njengotshani bomhlaba\x + Jobe 5.25.\x*.
